{"tid":2144758,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭若驊與夫持上市公司逾半股權或被制裁","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T00:20:16.000Z","uid":134683,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f196624f527cc7b88bfdc1930c128b13020ce661","tid":2144758,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"被制裁的11人之中，有人揚言對美方制裁「無畏無懼」，聲稱在美國無資產，但亦有人可能有切身影響。根據港交所資料，安樂工程今年5月發佈的最新年報顯示，律政司司長鄭若驊與丈夫潘樂陶，持有上市公司安樂工程（上市編號：1977）63.48%股份，屬控股大股東。按照美國財政部說法，被制裁者無論是直接或間接持有50%或以權益的財產，就已屬制裁範圍，換言之，安樂工程很可能成為被波及的港企。<br />\n<br />\n根據安樂工程最新年報，該集團今年3月以2.78億港元，收購了美國紐約市升降機公司Transel Elevator &amp; Electric Inc.（簡稱TEI）51%股份，涉資約2.78億元。由於安樂工程是TEI大股東，日後或無法在美國經營。翻查資料，律政司去年曾向傳媒表示，鄭若驊在安樂工程並無實益股份，亦沒參與該公司運作，但未知有關說法，是否為美國財政部所接納。"},{"pid":"f3f0ef08eee0c9addc265233730a390727317e24","tid":2144758,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/SBPJBEEFJY2WVC7FPTKG4XIKJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FSBPJBEEFJY2WVC7FPTKG4XIKJM%2F&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6HjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=72b07340\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200807%2FSBPJBEEFJY2WVC7FPTKG4XIKJM%2F&h=7357019a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200807/SBPJBEEFJY2WVC7FPTKG4XIKJM/</a>"},{"pid":"7369457ae8759f2f84e6365e8dd8f803c4ede5bb","tid":2144758,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a9e7f88bfe7794c13a5da52793de6601d7f20b","tid":2144758,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"係香港 你就話可以隻手遮天 係美國呢<br />\n你套口交部說法就<img src=\"/assets/fa